headline: LyondellBasell: This Dividend Yield Is Unsustainable
summary: With $13.3 billion in debt and a 12.3% forward dividend yield, LyondellBasell's dividend sustainability and financial flexibility are increasingly questionable. Learn more on LYB stock here.

headline: Compass (CMP) Soars 8.8%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: Compass (CMP) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.
